        <h2 class='abstract-title'>MapLibre – Out of the (Map)box. Wenn Open Source plötzlich Closed Source ist</h2>
        <section>
            <p>
                <span class='abstract-sessiontype'>Langer Vortrag</span>                von <span class='abstract-speakers'>Marcel Normann, Luke Seelenbinder, Petr Pridal</span></p>
